question: Which fast food restaurant can I find towards Daniel Cooney Fine Art Gallery, New York, NY within 100 kilometers from Science Hall West, Wayne, NJ?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-74.197766 40.946744)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-74.003635 40.749708)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-74.197766 40.946744)',4326)::geography, 100000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-74.197766 40.946744)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
